<p><span><b>Citing the database</b></span></p>
<p><span>If you use data from this website in publications, please cite this website, preferably as below:</span></p>
<p><span>&quot;This publication made use of the University of Oslo's <i>Bacillus cereus</i> group MultiLocus and MultiData Typing website (http://mlstoslo.uio.no)&quot;</span></p>

<p><span><b>Database implementation</b></span></p>
<p><span>The databases are constructed by using mlstdbNet software developed by <a href="http://www.biomedcentral.com/1471-2105/5/86/abstract" target="Index">Jolley et al, 2004</a>, heavily modified by Dr. Nicolas J. Tourasse, and the PostgreSQL database management system. The website makes use of  the facilities and support provided by the <a target="Index" href="http://www.biotek.uio.no/EMBNET/">Norwegian EMBnet node</a> and the <a target="Index" href="http://hpc.uio.no/">HPC</a> Supercomputing facilities at the University of Oslo.<br><a href="http://www.postgresql.org/" target="Index"><IMG SRC="images/PostgreSQL_logo.gif" WIDTH="88" HEIGHT="31" ALT="PostgreSQL"></a></span></p>

